Akeelah and the Bee;;81;;85;;PG;;Akeelah, an 11-year-old girl living in South Los Angeles, discovers she has a talent for spelling, which she hopes will take her to the National Spelling Bee. Despite her mother's objections, Akeelah doesn't give up on her goal. She finds help in the form of a mysterious teacher, and along with overwhelming support from her community, Akeelah might just have what it takes to make her dream come true.;;Kids & family,Drama;;Doug Atchison;;2006;;Laurence Fishburne,Angela Bassett,Keke Palmer,Curtis Armstrong,Tzi Ma,Lee Thompson Young,Dalia Phillips,Craig Wasson,J.R. Villarreal,Sean Michael Afable,Sara Niemietz,Eddie Steeples,Julito McCullum,Erica Hubbard,Sahara Garey;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/akeelah_and_the_bee